{{see|xerox}}

==English==
===Etymology===
From '''Xerox'''{{tm}}, the trademark name for a type of [[photocopier]], via ''[[xerography]]'' from Greek ''xero'' meaning dry and ''graphy'' meaning writing

===Noun===
'''Xerox'''
# A Xerox brand [[photocopier]].
#: ''Our new photocopying machine is a Xerox.''

